Text: Another great UP.  Thanks as always.
Thanks -- I already have most but not all of these, and my wife and I just got back from IM3 (a really GREAT time if you are willing to put aside "comic canon" and enjoy it for what it is).
A win to another great torrent! Thanks STF!

Hi, Everyone! Just a friendly reminder that today (Sat., May 1, 2013) is international Free Comic Book Day (FCBD)!!! Support your local comic book shop and pick up some freebies and meet other comic book fans, artists, and writers. -- Enjoy :)
